  entryDescription: I hear the cries of a baby...
  entryLore: "Found a crying baby once in the middle of the night. It wasn\u2019t
    really a baby\u2013\u2013 just a bald goblin disguised as one, with a hunger
    for fresh meat. It lured me with its cries, though I escaped. If you hear or
    see one, RUN. It\u2019s a trap."
